ont></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uparticleboy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>particleboy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 3:11:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> For some reason this gem is really hard to find on my server.  Lots of people buying but noone selling.  I need it for kael chain gloves (and I think casters need it for their gloves too).  Does any zone or creatures within a zone have a greater tendency to produce this gem?  Preferably something single group.<br><br>I think a lot of the gems on our server come from people killing spiders in Velks.  If so then I assume crushed topaz isn't dropping from the spiders otherwise we'd have a lot more.  Or is this just a problem of melees and casters both wanting it for an armour piece?  Personaly I can't see that because people need two bracers and CFEs on our server aren't as hard to find as crushed topaz is.<br><br>Any help appreciated.<br><br>More generally, does anyone know a resource on the web that details what Velious gems are dropped in which zone by which mob and the relative rarity? That would be really great.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uplaytorv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PlayTorv</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 3:27:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> ive gotten 3 or 4 from velks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uniqlamor2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>niqlamor2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 3:29:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> Suits of sentient armor.<br>Geonids.<br>Bulthars in CS. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustixum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stixum</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 6:45:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> Somewhat common in Sirens as well.  Got 3-4 in about a 2 hour period not to long ago. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utaralis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taralis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 7:40:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> Sirens in Siren's Grotto.<br><br><br>Near the well, I think. While farming them for BP gems, we got a TON of crushed topaz. It seemed that if we didn't get a BP gem, we'd get a crushed topaz or crushed flame emerald.<br><br><br>Crushed Topaz also seem to be somewhat rare on Torv. Not because they don't drop but because the armor pieces they're needed for are probably the most common drops in Kael/HoT/West Wing and the fact that they're used for both melee and casters. Plus, Sirens is a gold mine for gems but it's still a ghost town whenever we go there so the supply isn't as high as it should/could be IMO.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udaegulmistweaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daegul Mistweaver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 11:28:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> For crushed anything our best spot has been SG.  The bulthors/molokars/ulthorks there drop crushed gems exclusively. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udarkomen42.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DarkOmen42</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 12:08:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> The siren's that drop BP gems don't drop any other gems.<br><br>Or were you killing a few different kinds of Sirens? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utaralis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taralis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 1:44:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to find crushed topaz</span><hr size=1> Siren Enticers and Seductresses. There's a corner right by the staircase that you get to by swimming through the tunnel from WW zone and down a little chute (with 1 siren and 2 bulthar/molkors at the bottom). Facing the staircase, 45 degrees to your left are two watery servants seemingly guarding a wall. There's a siren spawn point on the left edge before a really slippery stretch (90-115 degrees from where you're standing). Shaman pulled Sirens from the area around the staircase (and up to 2 levels above us). Sirens dropped Flawless Diamonds/Black Marble/Pristine Emeralds and also Crushed Black Marble, Crushed Topaz, Crushed Flame Emerald, and Crushed Coral, in addition to the other drops (horns, necklaces, drums, etc).<br><br>Might have been different sirens than you're thinking of. One thing that might set them apart is, the ones we regularly pulled from the first and second levels didn't charm at all, they cast shiftless deeds (slow) and nukes but no charm. The ones pulled from the third (top?) level charmed almost constantly.<br><br>Crushed gems in addition to BP gems. In fact, crushed gems were a bit more common than the BP gems, from what we saw.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showPrevMessage?topicID=10596.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showNextMessage?topicID=10596.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10596.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.emailToFriend?topicID=10596.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.threadControl?topicID=10596.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=10596.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=10596.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump